<h1>Documentation</h1>
<h2>The JetSetter Project</h2>
<p>
    Visiting and exploring different countries is now a staple in this modern world. With the rise of social media, our project aims to
    provide a service to everyone,
    whether they want to showcase their travel destinations for other people or to just keep a private travel journal.
    We connect these people to businesses who can advertise products and services on our site.
</p>

