    <ul>
        <li>Make Account - Register and Log In (Securely)</li>
        <li>Manage Account</li>

        <li>
            Create Advertisments
            <ul>
                <li>Image</li>
                <li>Description</li>
                <li>Website</li>
            </ul>
        </li>

        <li>Modify and delete Ad posts</li>
        <li>
            Access to Home View
